relatedBlades.title: Cloudflare CDN
relatedBlades.subtitle: A global, enterprise-grade content delivery network (CDN)
relatedBlades.copy: Backed by %{DataCenterCount} locations worldwide, our CDN optimizes static and dynamic content for device, browser, and bandwidth needs.

contentfulAsset.description: DO NOT REMOVE, THIS IS CLOUDFLARE'S GLOBAL OG META ASSET

columnContent.title: Massive scale
columnContent.description: Our CDN supports global content delivery with a network that spans over %{DataCenterCount} locations.

columnContent.title: Faster applications and user experience
columnContent.description: Our CDN serves content as close to your end-users as possible — within approximately %{OperationMilliseconds} milliseconds of ~%{GlobalInternetConnectedPercent}% of the Internet-connected population — resulting in faster load times and a better web experience.

columnContent.title: Lower bandwidth and egress costs
columnContent.description: Our CDN helps reduce your hosting fees by reducing requests to your origin server and minimizing bandwidth usage.

relatedBlades.title: Increase content availability and redundancy
relatedBlades.copy:
Our CDN runs every service on every server in every Cloudflare data center — ensuring that content is served to end users from the closest available location.

The breadth of our [global network](https://www.cloudflare.com/network/) allows us to deliver static and dynamic content at the highest scale, while simultaneously maximizing performance and resiliency.

relatedBlades.title: Learn about the three challenges of securing and connecting application services

features.description: Cloudflare has been recognized as Leader and Outperformer in the 2024 GigaOm Radar for CDN report.

features.description: Cloudflare named a 'Leader' in 2024 IDC MarketScape for Worldwide Edge Delivery Services.

content.value: "Switching to Cloudflare, our system was 27% faster overnight. It improved our performance right off the bat — cache rates jumped immediately and things just started flowing."

relatedBlades.title: The Cloudflare CDN helps you develop fast, reliable applications while lowering costs and enhancing your user experience

columnContent.title: Modernize applications
columnContent.description: Develop and serve applications at the edge of our network to ensure better reliability and performance, even during unexpected traffic surges.

columnContent.title: Improve user experience
columnContent.description: Simplify your deployments and infrastructure for better scalability and an optimized user experience.

columnContent.title: Lower operational costs
columnContent.description: Eliminate hidden costs — like hardware refreshes and egress fees — to reduce your overall TCO.

planFeatures.name: Web Application Firewall (WAF)
planFeatures.description: Cloudflare Web Application Firewall's intuitive dashboard enables users to build powerful rules through easy clicks and also provides Terraform integration. Every request to the WAF is inspected against the rule engine and the threat intelligence curated from protecting millions of websites. Suspicious requests can be blocked, challenged or logged as per the needs of the user while legitimate requests are routed to the destination, agnostic of whether it lives on-premise or in the cloud.
